-- Khodorkovsky, Lebedev Found Guilty of Oil Theft by Moscow Court, IFX Says
-- B y   T o r r e y   C l a r k
-- 2010-12-27T08:12:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-27/khodorkovsky-lebedev-found-guilty-of-oil-theft-by-moscow-court-ifx-says.html
A Moscow court found Mikhail
Khodorkovsky, the jailed former head of Yukos Oil Co., and his
former business partner Platon Lebedev guilty of oil theft in
their second trial, while dropping some charges, Interfax
reported from the court room.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
